                      </div> 
                      <div class="ocr-faq-item__header--title"> 
                       <div class="lead "> 
                        <div data-oc-token-text=""> 
                         <h3><span class="d-block h5">I have a Hotmail.com, Live.com, or MSN.com email account. Is that the same as Outlook?</span></h3> 
                        </div> 
                       </div> 
                      </div> </button> 
                    </div> 
                    <div class="ocr-faq-item__body-wrapper collapse " id="accordion-inpage-oc84f7-item_1707221809237"> 
